  {
    id: 'prompt-28',
    prompt: 'Create a detailed contact list of emergency resources including crisis hotlines, safe housing options, and 24/7 support services in your area',
    category: 'planning',
    helpText: 'Having immediate access to crisis resources provides crucial security and peace of mind throughout your coming out journey, especially during emotionally challenging moments. Compile phone numbers for LGBTQ+ crisis hotlines, local emergency shelters or housing services, and 24/7 mental health support lines in your phone contacts with clear, recognizable names. This preparation ensures you can quickly access professional help if you encounter rejection, family conflict, or emotional crisis, providing a safety net that allows you to take authentic steps with greater confidence.'
  }
];</parameter>
<parameter name="new_string">  },
  {
    id: 'prompt-28',
    prompt: 'Create a detailed contact list of emergency resources including crisis hotlines, safe housing options, and 24/7 support services in your area',
    category: 'planning',
    helpText: 'Having immediate access to crisis resources provides crucial security and peace of mind throughout your coming out journey, especially during emotionally challenging moments. Compile phone numbers for LGBTQ+ crisis hotlines, local emergency shelters or housing services, and 24/7 mental health support lines in your phone contacts with clear, recognizable names. This preparation ensures you can quickly access professional help if you encounter rejection, family conflict, or emotional crisis, providing a safety net that allows you to take authentic steps with greater confidence.'
  },
  {
    id: 'prompt-29',
    prompt: 'Schedule and complete a professional consultation with an LGBTQ+-knowledgeable legal advisor to understand your rights and prepare legal documents',
    category: 'planning',
    helpText: 'Understanding your legal rights and having proper documentation prepared provides essential security and protection throughout your coming out journey and beyond. A knowledgeable legal advisor can explain anti-discrimination protections, help you prepare important documents like wills, healthcare directives, and power of attorney forms, and advise on name or gender marker changes if relevant. This proactive planning ensures your legal affairs are secure and your wishes are protected, giving you confidence to live authentically while safeguarding your interests.'
  }
];</parameter>
</invoke>
