<parameter name="old_string">    helpText: 'Preparing for identity challenges builds resilience and confidence for real-world situations where your authenticity may be questioned or dismissed. Work with a supportive friend to practice calm, clear responses to common invalidating comments while maintaining your emotional boundaries and self-worth. This preparation helps you stay centered during difficult interactions and ensures you have practiced language to assert your identity with dignity and strength.'
  }
