<parameter name="new_string">    helpText: 'Preparing for identity challenges builds resilience and confidence for real-world situations where your authenticity may be questioned or dismissed. Work with a supportive friend to practice calm, clear responses to common invalidating comments while maintaining your emotional boundaries and self-worth. This preparation helps you stay centered during difficult interactions and ensures you have practiced language to assert your identity with dignity and strength.'
  },
  {
    id: 'prompt-38',
    prompt: 'Document and organize your personal coming out story into key chapters, including important realizations, challenges overcome, and support received for future reference',
    category: 'action',
    helpText: 'Creating a personal narrative of your coming out journey helps you process your experiences, recognize your growth, and prepare to share your story with others when appropriate. Write down significant moments, turning points, and lessons learned in an organized format that you can reference for confidence or share with trusted people who want to understand your experience. This documentation serves as both personal validation and a resource for helping others or advocating for LGBTQ+ understanding in your community.'
  }
];</parameter>
</invoke>
